      "title": "Obsidian Vault Sync",
      "subtitle": "Markdown workspace as a derived/editing surface",
      "links": ["l7", "l8"],
      "steps": [
        { "title": "Export vault", "body": "M3E map を Markdown vault に export する。通常正本は SQLite workspace 側に残る。", "links": ["l7"] },
        { "title": "Import edits", "body": "vault 側編集を import して M3E map に戻す。V4 demo では export / edit / import を確認済み。", "links": ["l8"] }
